== Enter Mouse

* Small
* Fast
* Too many dependencies

+ 1 is too many!
----
== Enter Mousse

* Mousse is Mouse::Tiny

+* With *ZERO* dependencies
---- pl
== Add one line to Makefile.PL

use inc::Module::Install;

all_from 'lib/PPW.pm';

use_mousse 'PPW::OO';

WriteAll;
